results.name: Travel Backpack 45L
results.description: A rugged, expandable, and brilliantly accessible carry-on travel backpack with top, side, front, and rear access via weatherproof zips. Meets international carry-on requirements but expands to a 45L gear hauler. Includes quick-access pockets, padded laptop and tablet sleeves, collapse capability to 35L, and a weatherproof 100% recycled 400D nylon canvas shell.

results.name: Everyday Messenger Bag
results.description: This bag features top, side, front and rear access for quick key and passport accessibility, expandable side pockets for bottles, padded sleeves, and a zippered mesh sleeve for compartment separation. It is built from a durable, weatherproof 400D nylon canvas, suited for all travel needs.

results.name: Everyday Backpack V1
results.description: Everyday sling bag ideal for quick-access, transportation, and organization of essentials. It features instant customization through FlexFold dividers, a padded tablet sleeve, quick inner access via a weatherproof zip, and a durable 400D nylon canvas shell.
